snippet.title: Johnny Depp vs Amber Heard analysis. Codependent, narcissistic, belligerent, overbearing...
snippet.description:
manipulative, vindictive, dishonest.
I have spoken about toxic people and toxic relationships in previous videos. I have talked about how important it is to remove those types of people from your life. The situation between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard now brought to light by the recently released recordings of their argument is a high profile example of exactly what I have been referring to. You cannot force someone else to change. You cannot will someone else to be who you want them to be. You can only change yourself and you must remove toxic people from your life.
